Metadata: Data formats and codes for the INPFC/NPAFC all-agency high seas salmon and steelhead tag recovery computer data file (1956-2005)

This document lists the formats and codes used since 1971 for the all-agency INPFC- NPAFC high seas salmon and steelhead tag recovery computer data file (1956-2005). A brief overview and history of the computer data file is provided.
